First uncomment these lines:

```lang-xml
&lt;!--
&lt;Connector port=&quot;8443&quot; protocol=&quot;HTTP/1.1&quot; SSLEnabled=&quot;true&quot;
maxThreads=&quot;150&quot; scheme=&quot;https&quot; secure=&quot;true&quot;
